00:51:15.749 --> 00:51:21.259
And that's positively received, even in politics.
If Barack Obama ever said something that made

00:51:21.259 --> 00:51:25.719
him seem like "I'm not confident," they'd
be like, "OK, why are you doing it, then?"

00:51:25.719 --> 00:51:29.489
&gt;&gt;David Brooks: OK. Well, I'd ask you to go
