00:52:10.809 --> 00:52:11.809
Women tend to be pretty accurate.

00:52:11.809 --> 00:52:12.809
&gt;&gt;FEMALE #2: Yeah.

00:52:12.809 --> 00:52:17.390
&gt;&gt;David Brooks: And so, you wanna be slightly
