00:52:33.279 --> 00:52:39.119
will bear 70% of the load you're supposed
to, you don't wanna say, “That's a fantastic

00:52:39.119 --> 00:52:40.380
bridge."

00:52:40.380 --> 00:52:45.240
And so, you do wanna build. I mean, you do
