00:52:56.380 --> 00:52:59.559
in public, they totally believe what they're
saying.

00:52:59.559 --> 00:53:06.549
But in private, they have an equally authentic
self which says, "That's 70% true." And so

00:53:06.549 --> 00:53:10.619
I think it's valuable to have those two selves.
And by the way, that's another theme of the

00:53:10.619 --> 00:53:16.039
research is that we don't have one self. We
have a whole variety of very authentic selves.

00:53:16.039 --> 00:53:21.559
And so that would be my fudged answer to you.

